 4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the electrician##1
 5. the egyptian is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the person who's sport is sailing is in an even position##4
 7. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left or right of the chinese##3
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is between the person who's sport is cricket and the freelancer##2
 9. the australian is on the right of the british##1
10. the australian is on the left or right of the owner of the goat##3
11. the australian is in an odd position##4
